# Folders whose names contain a trailing space (mistaken `mkdir`)
# This is intentionally broad so any future naming accident is
# caught before being added to the repo.
Complex */
Complex* /

# Terraform state and variable files. `*.tfstate` and `*.tfstate.backup`
# are Terraform's default local-state filenames; `terraform.tfvars` is
# the auto-loaded var file and can contain secrets. `*.tfplan` files
# can contain rendered secrets too.
terraform/.terraform/
terraform/*.tfstate
terraform/*.tfstate.*
terraform/*.tfplan
terraform/terraform.tfvars
terraform/.terraform.lock.hcl.bak

# Vitest cache + coverage artifacts.
.vitest-cache/
coverage/
.vitest/

